   Win A Free Vacation!
   [blank.gif]
   We want to know more about you. Click here to win a free vacation to
   New Hampshire!
   How to Reach Us
   We'd love to hear from you. Please let us know your thoughts on our new
   site, comments about our state, or if we can be of any assistance in
   your travels to, and throughout, New Hampshire.
   Mailing Address:
   State of New Hampshire Division of Travel and Tourism Development
   172 Pembroke Road
   P.O. Box 1856
   Concord, New Hampshire 03302-1856
   Fax: 603-271-6870
   travel@dred.state.nh.us
   To order your vacation kit please call: 1-800-FUN-IN-NH ext. 169
   To speak with one of our Division office staff please call:
   1-603-271-2665
   Advertise with us!
   Travel and tourism brings more than $9.7 billion into our economy each
   year. As a New Hampshire business there are opportunities to promote
   yourself to these visitors through our state publications: The Official
   New Hampshire Guidebook, The New Hampshire Visitor's Guide, The Events
   Guide, and on this site www.visitnh.gov. Call or email us for more
   information at 603-356-8118 or sales@glengroup.com.
